# Custom ABC script for delay-aware sky130 mapping.
# {D} is substituted by yosys from `abc -D <picoseconds>`.
#
# Flow:
#   1) AIG cleanup / fraig / scorr
#   2) Delay-aware retime toward period
#   3) choice + &nf map under delay target
#   4) buffer tree + upsize / dnsize (needs -constr)
#   5) report ABC's internal timing (stime)

strash
&get -n
&fraig -x
&put
scorr
dc2
dretime
retime -o {D}
strash
&get -n
&dch -f
&nf {D}
&put
buffer
upsize {D}
dnsize {D}
stime -p
